<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1921-12-13T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1921-12-13T18:00:00-05:00" n="597" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d597">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">891.6363 Standard Oil/65: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Chargé in Persia</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Engert</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-12-13T18:00:00-05:00"><hi rend="italic">December 13,
                                        1921—6 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>44. Your 78 December 9, 9 P.M.</p>
                        <p>Department knows of no rivalry. Endeavor discreetly and if possible in
                            cooperation with Thompson to prevent any local appearance of
                            rivalry.</p>
                        <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>